messages.message:
While it is the position of most, if not all of the Pro-Life movement that life begins at conception,  there are also varying and less rigid positions from Pro-Choice to support the argument.

* Viability- where life becomes viable outside the womb;
* Quickening- where the unborn begins to move in the womb;
* Brainwaves- where brainwave activity becomes measurable;

These three positions, with no exceptions, are always past 16-20 weeks, after which the mother has undergone many changes and grown to appreciate the baby within.
